==English==

===Etymology===
Named after the German physicist Heinrich Rudolf Hertz.

===Noun===
'''hertz'''  (''plural:'' '''[[hertz]]''')
# In the [[International System of Units]], the [[derived unit]] of [[frequency]]; one ([[period]] or cycle of any [[periodic]] event) per [[second]].  Symbol: [[Hz]]

====Synonym====
*[[cycle per second]]

